title: MealPal CEO on Launch of Free Delivery Service
itunes:title: MealPal CEO on Launch of Free Delivery Service
description:
MealPal CEO Mary Biggins discusses the launch of her company's free delivery service. She also talks about ways restaurants are increasing meal preparation efficiency.

Host: Carol Massar. Producer: Doni Holloway.
